{"tid":1537393,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"湯家驊：公安條例容許特首委任「特務警察」增人手","createTime":"2019-09-04T02:07:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T02:55:22.000Z","uid":56881,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"f8ca85d5223c951110b87973e3c5e6206f53da35","tid":1537393,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:07:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B9%AF%E5%AE%B6%E9%A9%8A-%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%89%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E5%AE%B9%E8%A8%B1%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E5%A7%94%E4%BB%BB-%E7%89%B9%E5%8B%99%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F-%E5%A2%9E%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%8B-012527068.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%25B9%25AF%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E9%25A9%258A-%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E5%25AE%25B9%25E8%25A8%25B1%25E7%2589%25B9%25E9%25A6%2596%25E5%25A7%2594%25E4%25BB%25BB-%25E7%2589%25B9%25E5%258B%2599%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F-%25E5%25A2%259E%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2589%258B-012527068.html&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3LktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=b9837530\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B9%AF%E5%AE%B6%E9%A9%8A-%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%89%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E5%AE%B9%E8%A8%B1%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E5%A7%94%E4%BB%BB-%E7%89%B9%E5%8B%99%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F-%E5%A2%9E%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%8B-012527068.html</a><br />\n<br />\n行政會議成員、資深大律師湯家驊表示，在處理反修例爭議問題上，對實施《緊急法》有保留，他提出可以設立新法例，又或者引用《公安條例》。<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊出席本台節目《千禧年代》時表示，《緊急法》在憲法上沒有問題，但不等於政治上沒有問題，認為對「一國兩制」在國際間可信度大大降低，這不是一時三刻可以處理，因此要非常審慎。<br />\n<br />\n他提出，設立新法例可以包括蒙面法，又或者引用《公安條例》，勒令不可在重要公眾設施作出妨礙主要樞紐行為；另外，《公安條例》容許行政長官授權，委任一些處理特別事務的人士當特務警察，增加檢控或文書工作的人手。他說，條文沒有列明一定只能委任本地人，但他看不到有任何工作適宜內地人士去做。<br />\n<br />\n11哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪即係話有武警呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"331e9dd190d884372ebf0f882e8634963942e530","tid":1537393,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:07:12.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5952e8f9330f98387862b3067aa207097ec2a313","tid":1537393,"uid":267425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:07:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>解散警隊 刻不容緩</strong></span></span><br />\n我屌曬你地老母快啲推第六大訴求<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536852\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536852</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fLDFcUN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfLDFcUN.jpg&h=350c6ca1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"540cbe02e6fbed569aece2109a659edb9ae27d46","tid":1537393,"uid":62749,"like":1,"dislike"